The paper discusses deep generative models and their manipulation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The specific applications mentioned, such as neural style transfer and few-shot classification, are commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions Bayesian inference, which is a common topic in graphics (cs.GR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
